This is the Software Development Kit (SDK) for the family of &sle;
products. It is a free of charge extension for partners and customers
working with &sls;, Desktop, and derived products.

&susemgr; Proxies extend large and/or geographically dispersed &susemgr;
environments to reduce load on the &susemgr; Server, lower bandwidth
needs, and provide faster local updates.
